    "On the other hand, the best recall value was obtained by Sauvola's local adaptive thresholding method.",
    "Precision is an evaluation function that decreases as negative phases are misrecognized as positive phases.",
    "It shows differences among the neural network models, with a tendency for precision to increase with the resolution of features concatenated during upsampling.",
    "U-Net, which concatenates features at all resolutions, has the highest value compared to the other models.",
    "The IoU, which evaluates the overall segmentation accuracy of these models, was highest for U-Net, reaching 94.6%."
